import React from 'react'
import { Item } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import './App.css';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const DEFAULT_IMAGE = 'https://miro.medium.com/max/550/1*TxgjUE2uJuiRUVVmE_kU6g.png'

const Post = ({ title, content, userId, id }) => {
    const urlDetail = `/${id}`

    const handleOnClick = () => {
        console.log(id)
    }

    return (
    <Item.Group>
        <Link to={urlDetail}>
            <Item onClick={handleOnClick} className="post">
                <Item.Image size='small' src={DEFAULT_IMAGE} />

                <Item.Content>
                    <Item.Header as='a'>{title}</Item.Header>
                    <Item.Meta>User id: {userId}</Item.Meta>
                </Item.Content>
            </Item>
        </Link>
    </Item.Group>

    )
}

export default Post
